00:01:31.730 --> 00:01:34.700
And when I started
this, honestly, I

00:01:34.700 --> 00:01:36.860
could not see what was coming.

00:01:36.860 --> 00:01:39.740
I really did not
think that something

00:01:39.740 --> 00:01:44.210
like a shutdown of the
